  ∴ Re-check all outputs for contradictions...

-- LLM evaluation:
--
-- C1 (sector/governance): Circle of Twelve = 2 reps × 6 sectors. History
-- explains 12 Prometheus decks as origin. RESOLVED. ✓
--
-- C2 (timeline): 2810-2847 construction, 2847 departure, +80 years = 2927
-- arrival. 2930-2955 station construction. All dates consistent. RESOLVED. ✓
--
