--   = 315,000 m². Enough for 240,000 m² of quarters + corridors. ✓
-- - 12,000 initial colonists → 50,000 by year 3000 (73 years of station life).
--   Growth rate: ~2% annual. High but plausible with medical advances and
--   intentional population growth policy for a new colony. ✓
--
-- No contradictions found.

  yield consistent ≡ true
  yield contradictions ≡ []
  yield severity ≡ "none"

